It did ſo, but after my hapleſs and hopeleſs deſcent to this infernal Lake, the juſt portion of my uſurped command; Eridamus an active nimble Spirit; by Pluto's expreſs order, being appointed our State-Scout or Emiſſary, (this relation is true upon my Naked Honour) he returned me a Paſquil

from the middle Region, writ by ſome ſtigmatizing pen (as what quil now not ſet a work to divulge my ſhame?) in theſe lines:



'Tis an ill wind does good to no man bring,To Oliver Protector, upon the Whirlwind. Sep. 3. 1658.


Which was made good by our uſurping King;

Whoſe braving pomp farr lighter then a feather

Flew in a Whirlwind, the Lord knows whither.
